      <title>健康保险公司与美国就网络攻击后的救济问题分道扬镳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/health-insurers-split-with-us-over-relief-after-change-healthcare-hack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于上个月的网络攻击继续阻碍数十亿美元的付款，医疗保险公司和美国政府官员预计将于下周举行会议，讨论如何协助现金短缺的医疗机构的分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/health-insurers-split-with-us-over-relief-after-change-healthcare-hack</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 15:03:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚央行行长表示数据为更大幅度降息铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/colombia-central-banker-says-data-paves-way-for-bigger-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚央行董事会成员表示，哥伦比亚通胀放缓和经济疲软需要更大幅度的降息，但政策制定者必须对未来的潜在风险保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/colombia-central-banker-says-data-paves-way-for-bigger-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易紧张局势持续，马克龙将在巴黎接待中国习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/macron-to-host-china-s-xi-in-paris-as-trade-tensions-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟与世界第二大经济体之间的贸易紧张局势持续存在，法国总统马克龙计划于春季在巴黎接待中国国家主席习近平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/macron-to-host-china-s-xi-in-paris-as-trade-tensions-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉任命前财务主管为布拉斯科董事会成员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lula-will-name-former-finance-chief-mantega-to-braskem-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦预计将任命前财政部长吉多·曼特加为 Braskem SA 董事会成员，因为政府力争在企业决策中发挥更大影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lula-will-name-former-finance-chief-mantega-to-braskem-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:03:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starmer Deepfake 与 X 之战凸显英国大选担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/battle-with-x-over-starmer-deepfake-highlights-uk-election-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[社交媒体公司 X 拒绝删除英国反对党领袖凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 的深度造假音频片段，这在工党内部敲响了警钟，提醒人们警惕大选前虚假信息的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/battle-with-x-over-starmer-deepfake-highlights-uk-election-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰考虑征召囚犯补充饱受战争摧残的军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ukraine-mulls-drafting-convicts-to-replenish-war-battered-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰立法者计划考虑一项允许监狱囚犯加入战争的法案，因为在俄罗斯最近取得进展后，该国正在寻求加强前线人力的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ukraine-mulls-drafting-convicts-to-replenish-war-battered-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:31:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
