    <item>
      <title>欧盟与埃及将加强关系作为投资计划的一部分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-egypt-to-strengthen-relationship-as-part-of-investment-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟准备将其与埃及的关系升级为“战略伙伴关系”，此举可能会为这个北非国家带来数十亿欧元的资金和投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/eu-egypt-to-strengthen-relationship-as-part-of-investment-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官裁定，如果首席检察官离职，威利斯可以继续审理特朗普佐治亚州案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官裁定，只要与富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯有恋爱关系的首席检察官内森·韦德下台，富尔顿县地方检察官法妮·威利斯就可以继续监督佐治亚州唐纳德·特朗普干预选举案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/trump-prosecutor-fani-willis-can-stay-on-georgia-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在恢复停火谈判的同时准备袭击拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在平民被撤离后，以色列战时内阁批准对加沙城市拉法发动袭击，这表明当局准备在停火谈判正在进行的情况下加大对哈马斯的打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/israel-prepares-rafah-evacuation-after-netanyahu-approves-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 12:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
